<L>__{interior bud's condo day night}
<A>__{in its first stage, darien supervising. it's expanse of white walls devoid of mouldings, a blank plaster canvas. the city views are great, the apartment identical to hundreds of other cookie cutter condos. several young artists are working on a neo classical mural on the long side of the living room. they are colorfully dressed, listening to a talking heads tape while they work. a carpenter who looks like a member of duran duran is installing a pair of old columns from urban archaeology on either side of the entrance to the living room while another fits a brass sink into an antique sideboard which has been turned into a bar.}
